\par 
\par TWENTY-FIVE YEARS ALONE.
\par 
\par Joaquin Miller's Quaint Sketch of the Lonely Denizen of an Island Off the Western Coast.
\par 
\par A GREAT deal has been written about the extraordinary little woman who lived all alone on one of our islands for nearly a quarter of a century, but some of the facts seem to have escaped notice. {\*\atrfstart 441950376}
I shall write them down here as briefly as possible for the use of the coming De Foe [sic]. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af31507\afs16 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs15\fs16\insrsid13979655 {\*\atrfend 441950376}{\*\atnid SS}{\*\atnauthor Sara Schwebel}\chatn 
{\*\annotation{\*\atnref 441950376}{\*\atndate -2025738852}\ltrpar \pard\plain \ltrpar\s16\ql \li0\ri0\sa160\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\contextualspace \rtlch\fcs1 \af31507\afs20\alang1025 \ltrch\fcs0 
\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af31507\afs16 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs15\fs16\insrsid13979655 \chatn }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af31507 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13979655 Girl Crusoe}}}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af31507 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2061097 
{\*\atrfstart 441950377}In the first place this woman, although an Indian, was almost white and of extraordinary intelligence and sensibility.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af31507\afs16 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs15\fs16\insrsid13979655 {\*\atrfend 441950377}{\*\atnid SS}
{\*\atnauthor Sara Schwebel}\chatn {\*\annotation{\*\atnref 441950377}{\*\atndate -2025738852}\ltrpar \pard\plain \ltrpar\s16\ql \li0\ri0\sa160\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\contextualspace \rtlch\fcs1 
\af31507\afs20\alang1025 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af31507\afs16 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs15\fs16\insrsid13979655 \chatn }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af31507 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13979655 Noble savage}}}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af31507 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2061097 
\par 
\par The late Dr. Brinkerhoff, of Santa Barbara, who attended her in her last illness, told me that he thought perhaps she was not of Indian extraction at all. But to get on with the facts.
\par 
\par When the Jesuit priests founded their settlement at Santa Barbara they began to gather in all the docile or friendly Indians and utilize as well as civilize them.
\par 
\par After some years they found out that one of the small islands lying off about twenty miles from their harbor of Santa Barbara was inhabited. {\*\atrfstart 441950378}
The priests visited the island and found the most intelligent and gentle people there that had yet been discovered on the continent. They were loyal, affectionate, and loved their narrow and lonely little home in the sea above all things}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af31507\afs16 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs15\fs16\insrsid13979655 {\*\atrfend 441950378}{\*\atnid SS}{\*\atnauthor Sara Schwebel}\chatn {\*\annotation{\*\atnref 441950378}{\*\atndate -2025738851}\ltrpar \pard\plain \ltrpar
\s16\ql \li0\ri0\sa160\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\contextualspace \rtlch\fcs1 \af31507\afs20\alang1025 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af31507\afs16 
\ltrch\fcs0 \cs15\fs16\insrsid13979655 \chatn }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af31507 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13979655 Noble savage}}}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af31507 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2061097 
. They had never visited the main land. They had no wood to build boats with, and so the long black and barren mountain of land away to the south was as inaccessible to them as is the moon to us.
\par 
\par {\*\atrfstart 441950379}They had queer little houses of stone on the one low cliff, and they were very skillful in spearing fish and capturing all sorts of sea birds. They made mocassins [sic] for their feet out of seal
skins, for seals were and are to this day so abundant there that you can scarcely walk about without treading on some of the little baby seals. And all along to right and left, as you pass by, you see the mild-eyed mother seal nursing her baby at her brea
st, as she half rests and reclines against a rock, and lifts her kind, human eyes to yours, as if to ask you please not hurt her little hairy baby.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af31507\afs16 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs15\fs16\insrsid13979655 {\*\atrfend 441950379}{\*\atnid SS}
